---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="API Docs" description="Документація JSON API для Наказу МОУ № 402.">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-6 mb-2">API Docs</h1>
  <p class="text-ink-500 mb-4">
    Машино-читабельний JSON API для Наказу МОУ № 402.
    Спека — <a class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-300 underline" href="/api/openapi.json">OpenAPI 3.1</a>.
    Корінь — <a class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-300 underline" href="/api/index.json">/api/index.json</a>.
  </p>

  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
    <a href="https://github.com/workflowcat/nakaz-402/tree/main/web/packages/nakaz-402"
       target="_blank" rel="noopener"
       class="block p-4 rounded-md border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800 hover:border-accent-500 hover:bg-ink-50 dark:hover:bg-ink-900">
      <div class="font-mono text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-300">📦 npm: nakaz-402</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-ink-500 mt-1">Typed fetch client, ~3 KB, zero deps. Works in browsers / Node / Deno / Bun / Workers.</div>
    </a>
    <a href="https://github.com/workflowcat/nakaz-402/tree/main/web/packages/nakaz-402-mcp"
       target="_blank" rel="noopener"
       class="block p-4 rounded-md border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800 hover:border-accent-500 hover:bg-ink-50 dark:hover:bg-ink-900">
      <div class="font-mono text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-300">🤖 MCP: nakaz-402-mcp</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-ink-500 mt-1">Model Context Protocol server. Plug into Claude / Cursor / Zed and ask questions about наказ in plain language.</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <details class="my-4 p-4 rounded-md border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800 bg-ink-50 dark:bg-ink-900">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium">Приклади curl</summary>
    <div class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm font-mono">
      <pre class="overflow-x-auto bg-white dark:bg-ink-950 p-3 rounded border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800">curl -s https://nakaz-402.vercel.app/api/order.json | jq</pre>
      <pre class="overflow-x-auto bg-white dark:bg-ink-950 p-3 rounded border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800">curl -s https://nakaz-402.vercel.app/api/amendments.json | jq '.items[0]'</pre>
      <pre class="overflow-x-auto bg-white dark:bg-ink-950 p-3 rounded border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800">curl -s https://nakaz-402.vercel.app/api/amendments/518.json | jq</pre>
      <pre class="overflow-x-auto bg-white dark:bg-ink-950 p-3 rounded border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800">curl -s https://nakaz-402.vercel.app/api/polozhennia/01-osnovy-organizatsii/01-zagalni-polozhennia.json | jq '.title, .body_markdown[:200]'</pre>
    </div>
  </details>

  <div class="rounded-md overflow-hidden border border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800">
    <rapi-doc
      spec-url="/api/openapi.json"
      render-style="read"
      show-header="false"
      allow-try="true"
      allow-server-selection="false"
      theme="dark"
      bg-color="#0a0a0f"
      text-color="#e8e8f0"
      primary-color="#7253ed"
      regular-font="-apple-system, system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Inter, sans-serif"
      mono-font="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace"
      style="height: 100vh; width: 100%;"
    ></rapi-doc>
  </div>

  <script is:inline src="https://unpkg.com/rapidoc/dist/rapidoc-min.js"></script>
</Layout>
